        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Channels</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
          <li>Google Ads: Search, Performance Max, YouTube, and remarketing.</li>
          <li>Meta Ads: Prospecting, Advantage+ Shopping/Placements, and retargeting stacks.</li>
          <li>LinkedIn Ads: ICP targeting with Lead Gen Forms, website retargeting, and ABM.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>

    <aside class="md:col-span-1">
      <div class="sticky top-8 space-y-6">
        <div class="rounded-xl border p-6">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4">What you get</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-green-600"></span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium">Funnel strategy</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">TOFU/MOFU/BOFU plan with budgets and offers.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-green-600"></span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium">Creative testing</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Systematic A/B tests on hooks, formats, and ads.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-green-600"></span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium">Conversion tracking</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Clean event setup for CAC, ROAS, and LTV reporting.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-green-600"></span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium">Weekly optimization</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Bids, negatives, audiences, and budget shifts.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border p-6">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4">Metrics we optimize</h4>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li>CAC and blended CAC</li>
            <li>ROAS and MER</li>
            <li>LTV by cohort</li>
            <li>CPM, CPC, CVR</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border p-6">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4">Need this service?</h4>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-black text-white px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-gray-800 transition">Start a project</a>
